T'as dit ça l'an dernier.

555
00:54:39,439 --> 00:54:40,872
C‘est vrai, je l'ai dit!

556
00:54:41,680 --> 00:54:42,635
On y va.

557
00:54:44,039 --> 00:54:44,949
Génial.

558
00:54:51,280 --> 00:54:52,076
