560
00:56:44,959 --> 00:56:46,597
Je te retourne la question.

561
00:56:47,280 --> 00:56:49,111
Tu as une chose qui m‘appartient.

562
00:56:50,160 --> 00:56:51,434
Rends-la-moi.

563
